if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('SMSDetail')
and type = 'U')
drop table SMSDetail
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: SMSDetail */
/*==============================================================*/
create table SMSDetail (
ID int identity(1,1),
CellNumber varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
SMSContent varchar(200) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS not null,
Priority int null constraint DF__SMSDetail__Prior__7D046EF2 default (0),
RetryCount int null constraint DF__SMSDetail__Retry__7DF8932B default (0),
CreateTime datetime null constraint DF__SMSDetail__Creat__7EECB764 default getdate(),
HandleTime datetime null,
Status int not null constraint DF__SMSDetail__Statu__7FE0DB9D default (0),
constraint PK_SMSDETAILS primary key nonclustered ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
go
